{"tid":2381188,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日經「亞洲300可投資指數」2月剔除7間中企","createTime":"2021-01-26T11:41:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-27T02:37:24.000Z","uid":75656,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"554147a1a295c0de84547356aa8aa433bd7e8d0e","tid":2381188,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-26T11:41:25.000Z","msg":"美國前總統川普去年簽署行政命令，禁止美國人投資中國解放軍所持有、控制的公司，隨著該行政命令已於本月11日生效，日本經濟新聞社（Nikkei）也將在2月2日起，將中國電信、中國聯通、中海油等7家中企，剔除出2017年發布的跨市場指數「亞洲300可投資指數」（Nikkei Asia300 Investable Index）。<br />\n<br />\n《日經新聞》報導，日本經濟新聞社今宣布，將配合前美國總統川普的行政命令，將中國電信、中國聯通、中國海洋石油、中國移動、中國鐵建、中國中車和中國交通建設公司，剔除出亞洲300可投資指數。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，根據亞洲300可投資指數的計算規則，即使成份股的數量降至低於300，該指數也不會添加新股。不過，在預計於今年6月進行的年度定期審核中，亞洲300可投資指數的成份股數量，將恢復至300檔。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3423050\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3423050&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv3obfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=045b3f4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3423050&h=5861a5fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3423050</a><br />\n<br />\n日經新聞:<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Announcements/Nikkei-Asia300-Investable-Index-to-drop-7-Chinese-stocks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FAnnouncements%2FNikkei-Asia300-Investable-Index-to-drop-7-Chinese-stocks&d=TIKlq4bXcOIiQck3m%2BQSv3obfi2nm8u4SjNJtTZF4Nk%3D&h=969312ab\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.nikkei.com/Announcements/Nikkei-Asia300-Investable-Index-to-drop-7-Chinese-stocks</a>"},{"pid":"1c30cec9b4da089a0942ec39dc581bc412986892","tid":2381188,"uid":82394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T02:32:39.000Z","msg":"日本接力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/nor